## ğŸ“ Project Structure

```
SHORTS_GENERATOR_FINAL/
â”œâ”€â”€ assets/music/background.mp3         # Background music used in the shorts
â”œâ”€â”€ output/                             # Auto-generated folder for episode assets
â”œâ”€â”€ check_channel.py                    # Verifies logged-in YouTube channel name
